      },
      "playbook_text": "SECURITY INCIDENT RESPONSE: 1) Analyze login anomalies to identify compromised accounts. 2) Trace lateral movement. 3) Check data access logs. 4) Lock compromised accounts. 5) Rotate exposed API keys. Do NOT rotate keys before identifying which are compromised — you'll cause an outage.",
